data.description: This 1525 sqft, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom split floor-plan home sits on the water in a cul-de-sac. This home features a side entry two car garage, large living room with high vaulted ceilings and recessed lighting/dining room combo and eat-in kitchen. The master bedroom sits off to the side of the living room. The master bathroom has double vanity sinks, garden tub, stand-up shower and separate toilet room. All appliances stay within the home; Refrigerator, Stove, Dishwasher, Microwave, Washer & Dryer, along with a built in sprinkler system. A large backyard with a patio covered lanai facing the pond. Oversized driveway gives you extra space with your vehicles with a side entry garage; restricted deeded community. This property is close to 295 and NAS Jacksonville.
